{"name":"Arcane Background (Magic)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>On taking this Edge, a character gains one die type in @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Spellcasting]{Spellcasting}.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Arcane Background (Magic)]{Arcane Background (Magic)}</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_phrvgu41m1d","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Ik4NGrn3XMmBHwc9"}
{"name":"Duelist III","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Assassins are trained killers who know how to kill even the toughest foes. They add +2 to damage rolls when their foe is @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Distracted and Vulnerable]{Vulnerable} or they have @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.The Drop]{The Drop}</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Duelist II"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ceovwsdga4w","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Prestige Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"InJUysZTLitQ8LNF"}
{"name":"Fast Mount","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Mounting or dismounting a horse counts as an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Actions]{action}. An adventurer with this edge can mount and dismount as a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Actions]{free action}, but may only perform one of each maneuver per round. Thus, the character could mount and dismount in one round, but he couldn't mount, dismount, and remount in the same round.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Rassilon Expansion II</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Riding d6+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nyz86xwgjxi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"IrYdfxGHp4UwAa8z"}
