{"name":"Favored Powers (Cleric)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The cleric has great familiarity with certain powers and can cast them quickly and easily. Once per turn, he may ignore up to two points of any penalties (@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions]{Multi-Actions}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Damage Effects]{Wounds}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigue}, etc.) when casting arcane <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Protection]{protection}, @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Healing]{healing}, @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Smite]{smite}</em>.</p>\n<p>This Edge doesn&rsquo;t give him those powers&mdash; they must be taken separately.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Cleric"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_rzst3tdjv7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Cleric","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Jw9NKpzSrB7HKsgV"}
{"name":"Strength Surge","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The barbarian&rsquo;s rage knows no bounds! Her @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Strength} increases two die types when raging instead of just one. This can exceed the character&rsquo;s racial limit.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Barbarian"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_uz53jzntey","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Barbarian","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"K9YFFwuwh9po4P3V"}
