{"name":"Master and Commander","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Crews who serve under these skilled leaders add +2 to their @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} rolls.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Smarts d8, Boating d10+, Intimidation d8+, Command, must be sole Captain of the vessel when the Edge is used"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_13m4lijdpgi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"dRuV7EijZViqdXkr"}
{"name":"A Few Good Men","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The character knows how to get the best from the troops at his disposal.</p>\n<p>Once the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Mass Battles]{tokens} for each force have been calculated, the character adds one token to his army's total to account for their status.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Inspire, Smarts d8+, Battle d10+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_13m4lijdpgi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ddMKqrusPvUvxNjw"}
