{"name":"Connection","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p><strong>Times may be taken: </strong>4</p>\n<p>At some point a hero is likely to gain Glory by aiding certain organizations, whether directly or indirectly. When a hero gains a Connection, he must pick a specific group, as per the Edge of the same name. The hero does not belong to the organization&mdash;he simply has friends among their number willing to assist him (though he may, at the GM&rsquo;s discretion, be offered membership as well).</p>\n<p>The Connection should be appropriate to the character&rsquo;s background and his deeds. For instance, a hero who slays many lycanthrope beasts likely attracts the attention of the Church of the Silver Flame, whereas one who stops an outbreak of disease caused by a plague demon might find House Jorasco are favorable toward him.</p>\n<p>Note that the hero still needs @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Persuasion]{Persuasion} and @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Networking]{Networking} for this benefit to be of any use. Just because he&rsquo;s renowned, it doesn&rsquo;t mean the Connection will drop everything and come to his aid with exactly what he wants.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"20+ Glory"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_xbof4ishapq","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Glory Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"iRhD7JOEPedb310j"}
{"name":"Filthy Rich","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This fortunate individual is inordinately wealthy. He starts with 1,500 gp and has a weekly income of 2d4 x 1,000 gp. Responsibilities increase dramatically as well, as such wealth requires a staff to manage the business, advisors, or a sizable retinue to take care of day-to-day matters, personal affairs, and other needs.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Rich"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_phrvgu41m1d","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Background Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"imqiV2yhsTKuGsV3"}
