{"name":"Martial Flexibility","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Once per encounter, as a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Actions]{free action}, a fighter can choose to gain the benefits of a single Combat Edge. He must meet all of the Edge&rsquo;s Requirements, and the benefits of the chosen Edge end after five rounds.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Fighter"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_cbe5u35c01","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Fighter","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"j210oxVviTpc7w6U"}
{"name":"Infuse Item","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Artificers study the arcane science and have learned how to harness magical energies into items. They may turn an ordinary blade into a magic sword, grant powerful potions to their friends, or imbue a belt that grants its wearer increased @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Strength}.</p>\n<p>Artificers can create <strong>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Devices]{Arcane Devices}</strong> and give them to their allies.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Artificer"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_58ynsuma4xq","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Artificer","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jF3LERPY1HeZsuzO"}
{"name":"Siege Breaker","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This Edge is used only for @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Mass Battles]{Mass Battles}. The hero has a good knowledge of siege warfare and can spot weaknesses in enemy fortifications.</p>\n<p>When he leads the army, the character reduces the Siege Bonus of any fortification his men are attacking by 1 (to a minimum of zero).</p>\n<p>If he makes a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Battle]{Battle} roll at the start of a siege, he can increase the Siege Bonus penalty by an additional &minus;1 for success and &minus;2 with a raise by studying and exploiting specific weaknesses.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Command, Smarts d8+, Battle d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_13m4lijdpgi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jrXQ1LZa4ioCHlrv"}
{"name":"Extreme Explorer II","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Assassins are trained killers who know how to kill even the toughest foes. They add +2 to damage rolls when their foe is @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Distracted and Vulnerable]{Vulnerable} or they have @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.The Drop]{The Drop}</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Extreme Explorer"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ceovwsdga4w","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Prestige Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"kBGjCMpm6H7pWRdd"}
