{"name":"Heroic Aura","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p><strong>Times may be taken: </strong>4</p>\n<p>True heroes have destinies beyond those of lesser men. As a hero becomes more famous, so his fate becomes more important. Lesser foes no longer present the danger they once did, and only the mightiest enemies give the hero pause.</p>\n<p>When not wearing armor (he may use a shield), he gains +1 @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Characters]{Toughness} each time he takes this benefit. While wearing armor, no benefit is gained. Encumbrance plays no part in this benefit&mdash;the modifier is gained even if the hero is heavily weighed down with other gear.</p>\n<p>In game terms, taking this benefit once grants the protection equivalent of cloth armor, but it cannot be reduced by @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Armor Piercing (AP)]{AP} weapons, protects against area effect attacks, and has zero encumbrance. With a second benefit, the hero as well protected as wearing light armor, three times medium armor, a fourth time heavy armor.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"40+ Glory"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_xbof4ishapq","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Glory Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ltZ207VrEpo444jo"}
{"name":"Charge","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The character knows how to deliver a well-aimed blow at the end of a charge.</p>\n<p>If the hero performs a run action and ends his movement for the round adjacent to an opponent, he may make a single @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} roll as a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Free Attacks]{free attack} (no @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions]{multi-action} penalty). This cannot be combined with @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Frenzy]{Frenzy} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Sweep]{Sweep}.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Rassilon Expansion II</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Vigor d8+, Fighting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_nyz86xwgjxi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"mM3WYk50fyHAPhz2"}
{"name":"Druidic Vow","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core\">\n<p>Druids have a major vow to serve and protect nature. Those who wish to draw energy from natural sources must uphold these principles.</p>\n<p>If the druid violates Eberron's trust (DM's call) the druid subtracts 2 from @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Faith]{Faith} rolls for a week. Truly sacrilegious acts might rob her of her powers entirely until she atones in some way.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":true},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_0j1u3hopqpse","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Druid","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"mUoS17oJqPhFiZpe"}
