{"name":"Master Hunter","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Rangers have now become deadly enemies of their chosen prey. They add an additional d6 damage when making a successful @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} (throwing), @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Fighting]{Fighting}, or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Shooting]{Shooting} attack against their @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Favored Enemy]{Favored Enemy}.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Ranger"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_y4rfdvvjk7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Ranger","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"siJ4TFzq1VAMZAGc"}
{"name":"Board 'Em","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The character is a master at judging when to launch grapples against enemy vessels. When he leads the boarding party group @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} rolls to grapple (@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Chases and Vehicles]{Board}) an enemy vessel receive a +4 bonus.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Command, Athletics d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_13m4lijdpgi","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"tIg9wafAMFaBbkk9"}
{"name":"Monk","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>For the truly exemplary, martial prowess transcends the battlefield&mdash;it is a lifestyle, a doctrine, a state of mind. Such warrior-artists search out methods of battle beyond swords and shields, finding weapons within themselves as lethal as any blade.</p>\n<p>These monks (so called since they adhere to ancient philosophies and strict martial disciplines) elevate their bodies to become weapons of war. Monks tread a path of discipline and balance &mdash;in mind, breath, and body.</p>\n<p>Monks gain the following abilities:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Monk Armor Restriction (Light)]{Monk Armor Restriction (Light)}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Stunning Fist]{Stunning Fist}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Unarmed Strike]{Unarmed Strike}</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d6+, Spirit d6+, Fighting d6+"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_7kugpblr0yu","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Monk","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"tZhZHGK6dlrFsMYJ"}
{"name":"Druid Armor Interference (Light)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Bulky armor interferes with a druid&rsquo;s ability to sense and commune with nature. They subtract 4 from their @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Faith]{Faith} rolls and from their @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility} and @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility-based} skill rolls when wearing medium or heavy armor, or using medium or heavy shields.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":false},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_0j1u3hopqpse","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Druid","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"tnv8ryRBi8PEkwcH"}
{"name":"Barbarian Armor Restriction (Medium)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>A barbarian&rsquo;s fighting style requires great freedom of movement. They subtract 4 from @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility} and @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility-based} skill rolls when wearing heavy armor or using a heavy shield.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":false},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_uz53jzntey","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Barbarian","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"tpf75LRghnMuDbyP"}
{"name":"Eldritch Knight III","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Assassins are trained killers who know how to kill even the toughest foes. They add +2 to damage rolls when their foe is @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Distracted and Vulnerable]{Vulnerable} or they have @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.The Drop]{The Drop}</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Eldritch Knight II"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ceovwsdga4w","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Prestige Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uCdle2hbCoLDrOjN"}
{"name":"Sorcery Mastery","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>True understanding of magical energy comes with practice and experience. Those who take this Edge gain access to all their powers&rsquo; Epic Power Modifiers.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Sorcerer"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_cna61w56xkj","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Sorcerer","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uV251TDcO1GS2Msu"}
{"name":"Eldritch Inspiration","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Great wizards gather esoteric information in their spellbooks, allowing them to harness magical powers at a whim. Assuming he has his spellbook on his person, the wizard can spend a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Bennies]{Benny} to cast any power of his @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Advancement]{Rank} or lower. The power may be maintained normally but afterwards is forgotten (the wizard doesn&rsquo;t add it to his list of powers).</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Wizard"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_6v947zso8xk","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Wizard","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ueVrpdQgkLVmOWBJ"}
{"name":"Ranger","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>For those who relish the thrill of the hunt, there are only predators and prey. From scouts, to trackers, or bounty hunters, all rangers share the predator&rsquo;s perspective. They value skill with weapons. They excel at stalking even the most elusive game. They train relentlessly to defeat a wide range of quarries.</p>\n<p>Knowledgeable, patient, and skilled hunters, rangers pursue man, beast, and monster alike. While some track dangerous creatures to protect the frontier, others pursue more cunning game&mdash;even fugitives&mdash;into and through the dangerous wilds.</p>\n<p>Rangers gain the following abilities:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Favored Enemy]{Favored Enemy}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Favored Terrain]{Favored Terrain}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Wilderness Stride (Ranger)]{Wilderness Stride}</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Shooting d6+, Survival d6+"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_y4rfdvvjk7","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Ranger","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vBkTcUlWxqEPryjK"}
{"name":"Homunculus","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The artificer crafts a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Homunculus]{homunculus} to assist it in tasks of his choice.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Artificer"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_58ynsuma4xq","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Artificer","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vRzVfQSoRtN5wh5A"}
{"name":"Favored Powers (Druid)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The druid has great familiarity with some of her core powers and can cast them quickly and easily. Once per turn, she may ignore up to two points of any penalties (@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions]{Multi-Actions}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Damage Effects]{Wounds}, @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigue}, etc.) when casting <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Entangle]{entangle}, @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Shape Change]{shape change}, @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Smite]{smite}, @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Protection]{protection}</em>.</p>\n<p>This Edge doesn&rsquo;t give her those powers&mdash; they must be taken separately.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Druid"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_0j1u3hopqpse","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Druid","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vhCpHjoXbqzCuqgB"}
