{"name":"Mark of Making","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>As a limited free action the dragonmarked heir can cast one of the following spells:&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\"><em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Conjure Item]{Conjure item}</em> (including Mythic Powers, not including Create Food and Water), <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Detect/Conceal Arcana]{detect/conceal arcana}</em> (not including Alignment Sense), <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Object Reading]{object reading}</em>, <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Repair]{repair}</em>, and <em>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Smite]{smite}</em>.</span></p>\n<p>The heir has 10 dedicated @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{Power Points} that recharge normally. He automatically activates the power with success for its regular cost, or with a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Trait Rolls]{raise} for an additional @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{Power Point}.&nbsp; He may use applicable Power Modifiers if desired.</p>\n<p>The Mark of Making doesn&rsquo;t grant access to Edges requiring an Arcane Background. If the heir also has an Arcane Background, none of its Edges, abilities, or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{Power Points} can be used with the Mark of Making (and vice-versa).</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Human"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_m9rojhhzc3m","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Dragonmarked Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zPSCcC6DN8XaBYWq"}
