{"name":"Monk Armor Restriction (Light)","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Monks must be&nbsp; unhindered to perform their complex maneuvers. They subtract 4 from @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility} and @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Agility-based} skill rolls when wearing medium, or heavy armor, or using&nbsp; medium, or heavy shields.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":false},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_7kugpblr0yu","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Class Edges#/CF_SEP/Monk","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zwEtVYDt9pg1htFH"}
{"name":"Mystic Theurge II","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Assassins are trained killers who know how to kill even the toughest foes. They add +2 to damage rolls when their foe is @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Distracted and Vulnerable]{Vulnerable} or they have @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.The Drop]{The Drop}</span></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Mystic Theurge"}},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ceovwsdga4w","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Prestige Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"m6EC20gvQByU17vc"}
